commit.message:
Updated secondsToString function

Removed hours count since the games likely won't extend that long, and removed leading zero before the minutes count.
Fixed bug with non-default values of game length, renamed GAME_LENGTH to gameLength

Image Resizing

Added image resizing so that no images exceed the specified width and height.
Added score feature, minor UI updates

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/NiamV/OxfordHack
Added skip button, which needs to be merged with the current branch that contains added equations.
